 nawigacji.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, nowe funkcje reklamowe na Amazonie, takie jak promowane posty i <a href=\"\/?p=5639\">reklamy wideo<\/a> w formacie pionowym, mog\u0105 znacz\u0105co wp\u0142yn\u0105\u0107 na Twoj\u0105 strategi\u0119 reklamow\u0105. Wykorzystaj te narz\u0119dzia, aby zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 swoj\u0105 obecno\u015b\u0107 i sprzeda\u017c na tym dynamicznym rynku.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Jak zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 efektywno\u015b\u0107 reklamy na Amazonie?<\/h2>\n<p>Czy zastanawia\u0142e\u015b si\u0119, jak poprawi\u0107 widoc<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":7726,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[4],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-7725","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-marketplace"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7725"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=7725"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7725\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/7726"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=7725"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=7725"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=7725"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp